<l>aṉpō ṭiyainta vaḻakkeṉpa vāruyirk</l>
<l>keṉpō ṭiyainta toṭarpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>They say that the union of soul and body in man is the fruit of the union of love and virtue (in a former birth).</l>
